---
title: Glazed Teriyaki Chicken with Bok Choy and Coconut Rice
description: Did someone say sticky chicken? The sweet and savoury combination of soy, honey, ginger and garlic makes a delicious teriyaki glaze. The glazed chicken is plated over a steamy bed of coconut rice with pops of bok choy. Cashews finish this dish off with a satisfying crunch!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/glazed-teriyaki-chicken-d55db9a2.jpg
